			<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Principle 2: <br>We are objective and use evidence</h1>
			<p>This principle is about <strong>taking an evidence-led mindset, and challenging biases</strong>.</p>
            <p>As a user researcher at DfE, it means that you use evidence to explain the problems you're trying to solve. You understand where bias and assumptions might impact your insights, always testing and mitigating against this. You do what's right, not what's popular. And you are efficient, by learning from and building on existing research and evidence.</p>

		    <div class="bordered-top--dark"></div>
